tripleo_ansible/roles/backup-and-restore.message:
+1 if we want to amend a file with content like this we might want to use blockinfile

  - name: Add extra ReaR config variables into the local.conf
    blockinfile:
      path: /etc/rear/local.conf
      block: |
        {% for k, v in (tripleo_backup_and_restore_extra_local_config | dict2items) %}
        {{ k }}={{ v }}
        {% endfor %}

Something like this will be faster and more sustainable.

